ARE YOU COMING?

42:27.345 --> 42:30.716
- YEAH.

42:30.749 --> 42:32.651
[cheers and applause]

42:32.684 --> 42:35.687
- UNCLE VIC.
UNCLE VIC.

42:37.322 --> 42:40.058
LONG LIVE THE QUEEN!

42:40.091 --> 42:41.893
- HMM.

42:41.927 --> 42:43.829
MELANIE'S THE ONE
YOU SHOULD BE CONGRATULATING.

42:43.862 --> 42:46.097
- OH, STOP.

42:46.131 --> 42:48.366
[applause]

42:48.399 --> 42:49.601
- WHOO!

42:49.635 --> 42:51.336
- SHE GOT MY CASE
THROWN OUT.

42:51.369 --> 42:53.972
- BUT YOU'RE THE ONE
WHO WAS SO BRAVE.

42:54.005 --> 42:55.040
- YOU WERE AN INSPIRATION,

42:55.073 --> 42:57.242
THE WAY YOU STOOD UP
FOR YOURSELF.

42:57.275 --> 42:59.210
- WELL,
AFTER THAT TERRIBLE STORY

42:59.244 --> 43:00.345
YOU TOLD ME
ABOUT THAT POOR MAN

43:00.378 --> 43:03.048
WHO WAS BURIED
IN AN UNMARKED GRAVE.

43:03.081 --> 43:04.816
- WHAT DID YOU TELL HIM?

43:04.850 --> 43:07.152
ONE OF YOUR SOUTHERN GOTHIC
HORROR STORIES?

43:07.185 --> 43:08.353
- MM.

43:08.386 --> 43:10.188
- YOU MEAN IT WASN'T TRUE?
- MM-MM.

43:10.221 --> 43:11.990
- ALL OF MY STORIES
ARE TRUE.

43:12.023 --> 43:13.291
- OH, JESUS.

43:13.324 --> 43:15.861
- AND IF THEY'RE NOT, THEY...
SHOULD BE.

43:15.894 --> 43:17.963
[laughter]

43:19.765 --> 43:23.068
- HE IS SO FUNNY.
I LOVE HIM.

43:24.736 --> 43:25.871
- NOW REMEMBER
WHAT WE SAID.

43:25.904 --> 43:28.306
WE'LL JUST STAY HERE
FOR A FEW MINUTES,

43:28.339 --> 43:30.208
THEN WE'LL GO HOME.

43:30.241 --> 43:31.209
- OKAY.

43:31.242 --> 43:34.045
GOTTA GO.

43:34.079 --> 43:35.046
- BYE, GUYS.
TAKE CARE.

43:35.080 --> 43:37.849
- BYE.
- SEE YOU GUYS.

43:37.883 --> 43:39.250
- BYE, MEL.
- YEAH.

43:39.284 --> 43:41.286
HEY, DO THE THING
WITH THE BREADSTICKS.

43:41.319 --> 43:43.855
[overlapping chatter]

43:43.889 --> 43:46.324
- NIGHT, EM, I'LL TALK
TO YOU TOMORROW. DEB, THANKS.

43:46.357 --> 43:47.392
[upbeat jazz]

43:47.425 --> 43:49.394
- * SAILING ON

43:49.427 --> 43:50.996
*

43:51.029 --> 43:53.965
* LIKE THE HAPPY RHYTHM

43:53.999 --> 43:54.966
* OF MY FAVORITE SONG

43:55.000 --> 43:56.367
- BYE.
CONGRATS.

43:56.401 --> 43:59.137
[overlapping chatter]

43:59.170 --> 44:02.273
- MEL, I'LL CALL YOU
TOMORROW ABOUT THAT THING?

44:02.307 --> 44:04.309
OKAY.

44:04.342 --> 44:06.377
NIGHT.
- THAT'S FINE, I JUST NEED...

44:06.411 --> 44:07.846
- I GUESS WE'LL HAVE
TO SAY SOMETHING.

44:07.879 --> 44:10.181
- WE'LL SEE YOU TOMORROW.
OKAY.

44:10.215 --> 44:12.684
- YEAH.
OKAY.

44:12.718 --> 44:14.385
- NIGHT, MIKEY.

44:14.419 --> 44:16.287
- I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

44:16.321 --> 44:18.156
- YEAH, YOU'RE RIGHT.
- * SAILING ON

44:18.189 --> 44:20.025
- WILL THEY WANT YOU
TO START RIGHT AWAY?

44:20.058 --> 44:22.360
- THOSE GUYS ON MADISON AVENUE
MOVE FAST.

44:22.393 --> 44:24.229
- SO DO THE ONES
IN CHELSEA.

44:24.262 --> 44:26.064
- THERE'LL BE PLENTY OF HEARTS
TO BREAK IN THE BIG CITY.

44:26.097 --> 44:29.034
- WELL, YOU DON'T HAVE
TO BREAK THEM ALL AT ONCE.

44:29.067 --> 44:31.036
AND CALL
EVERY ONCE IN A WHILE.

44:31.069 --> 44:32.203
- LIKE THAT'LL HAPPEN.

44:32.237 --> 44:33.471
- DON'T MAKE US ALWAYS
HAVE TO CALL YOU.

44:33.504 --> 44:36.074
- WHY DON'T YOU ALL
JUST SHUT THE FUCK UP?

44:36.107 --> 44:38.910
- * I'LL BE SAILING ALONG

44:38.944 --> 44:42.347
- I NEED A CIGARETTE.

44:42.380 --> 44:43.414
- * ROW, ROW,
ROWING ALONG *

44:43.448 --> 44:46.317
- AND HERE'S
OUR HOUSE BOURBON.

44:46.351 --> 44:51.189
*

44:51.222 --> 44:52.257
- THANKS.

44:52.290 --> 44:58.229
[indistinct chatter]

45:02.968 --> 45:04.069
YOU'RE A LUCKY GUY.

45:04.102 --> 45:06.071
- I AM?

45:06.104 --> 45:07.438
- EVERYTHING YOU'VE GOT.

45:07.472 --> 45:10.341
ALL YOUR FRIENDS
AND YOUR FAMILY.

45:10.375 --> 45:14.145
- YEAH, I KNOW.

45:14.179 --> 45:15.480
- IF YOU DECIDE
TO GO WITH ME,

45:15.513 --> 45:18.416
YOU KNOW, YOU'D BE LEAVING
A LOT BEHIND.

45:20.551 --> 45:23.889
- IT'S A--
IT'S A HUGE DECISION.

45:23.922 --> 45:26.024
- WELL, TAKE YOUR TIME,

45:26.057 --> 45:28.159
THINK ABOUT IT.

45:28.193 --> 45:31.262
BUT IF YOU DECIDE
NOT TO GO...

45:34.532 --> 45:38.336
I'LL BE VERY UPSET.

45:38.369 --> 45:43.008
BUT I'LL UNDERSTAND.

45:43.041 --> 45:47.245
[indistinct chatter]

45:47.278 --> 45:50.148
- I'VE DECIDED.

45:53.251 --> 45:55.253
I WANT TO GO.

45:57.889 --> 45:59.357
- YOU'RE SURE?

45:59.390 --> 46:01.426
- [chuckles]
NO.

46:13.338 --> 46:16.407
[Jamie Oakes's
Go to the Water]

46:16.441 --> 46:21.813
- * SO MANY PRISONERS

46:21.847 --> 46:25.383
* LOCKED TO THE CLOCK

46:25.416 --> 46:28.086
*

46:28.119 --> 46:33.191
* SO MANY CHANCES TO SEE

46:33.224 --> 46:39.030
* WHAT YOU HAVE
AND WHAT YOU ARE NOT *

46:39.064 --> 46:44.569
* YOU GO TO THE WATER

46:44.602 --> 46:50.175
* GO ON YOUR HANDS
AND KNEES *

46:50.208 --> 46:55.413
* SEE WHAT IT GIVES YOU

46:55.446 --> 46:57.916
* WELL, ARE YOU SO HARD

46:57.949 --> 47:03.121
* TO PLEASE?

47:03.154 --> 47:11.062
*

47:12.931 --> 47:18.569
* 200 HOURS

47:18.603 --> 47:24.342
* AND NEXT MONTH
WILL BE THE SAME *

47:24.375 --> 47:29.948
* TIME IS A LINE
ON YOUR FACE *

47:29.981 --> 47:35.486
* TIME IS LIFE
SLIPPING AWAY, BUT... *

47:35.520 --> 47:41.226
* GO TO THE WATER

47:41.259 --> 47:46.898
* GO ON YOUR HANDS AND KNEES

47:46.932 --> 47:52.470
* SEE WHAT IT GIVES YOU

47:52.503 --> 47:54.572
* WELL, ARE YOU SO HARD

47:54.605 --> 48:00.245
* TO PLEASE?

48:00.278 --> 48:08.286
*
